animeTitle: Tsun Tsun Maid wa Ero Ero Desu
animeDescription: Eishun's busty, tsundere childhood friend, Kiriha, becomes his personal maid. After secretly taking pictures of her in her maid outfit, Eishun ends up getting caught masturbating to them by Kiriha.
